{
  "stem": "16214.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the one ulpan that was available at the time, I can't even recall the name of it right now.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this ulpan had kids my age, and perhaps year older or so from Africa.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there were no European Jews with exception of me and another girl.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were in this ulpan.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now there was such a big difference, cultural shock, between us and these other kids that it was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, we were extremely naive at the age of 15.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We would not go out with boys.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was something, I mean, you were just-- I was still a little girl, really, never wore any makeup, no lipstick, no high-heeled shoes, no-- I mean this was just very naive little kids really.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, you know, one night we're there, you know, the first like-- it was maybe the second night or so.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "These girls and boys would get together in the middle of the night, and they would be making love and stuff.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they would have fights.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they fought over some girl that we had no idea, in our room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Me and my other friend from Poland, we started, we were so terrified, so scared, we hid under our beds.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And the guys started slashing each other because of that girl.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were totally-- I mean, dumbfounded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It's-- it was something unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And after two hours of this whole thing, you know, finally someone, some adult heard, and came around and separated the group, and started collecting the injured, and et cetera.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it was a terrifying thing for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The following day, you know, I-- I just-- I was very, very quiet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I said, I'm not going to go to that room again.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
